config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    primaryColor: "#4A90D9"
    primaryTextColor: "#000"
    lineColor: "#555"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant HOST as 上位机 (Web Dashboard)
    participant SERIAL as USB转串口
    participant SLAVE as STM32F407<br/>Modbus RTU 从站
    participant REG as 保持寄存器<br/>g_modbus_registers[58]
    participant HW as 硬件外设<br/>(PWM/ADC/MS901M)

    Note over HOST,HW: === 连接阶段 ===

    HOST->>SERIAL: Web Serial API<br/>请求串口 9600 8N1
    SERIAL-->>HOST: 连接成功

    Note over HOST,HW: === 读取数据 (FC03) ===

    HOST->>SERIAL: TX: [01 03 00 00 00 06 CRC]<br/>读系统寄存器 0x0000~0x0005
    SERIAL->>SLAVE: USART2 RX
    SLAVE->>REG: eMBRegHoldingCB()<br/>mode=MB_REG_READ
    REG-->>SLAVE: 返回 6 个寄存器值
    SLAVE-->>SERIAL: TX: [01 03 0C data... CRC]
    SERIAL-->>HOST: 解析响应, 更新 UI

    HOST->>SERIAL: TX: [01 03 00 10 00 0C CRC]<br/>读姿态寄存器 0x0010~0x001B
    SERIAL->>SLAVE: USART2 RX
    SLAVE->>REG: 读取 12 个寄存器<br/>(6个 IEEE754 float)
    REG-->>SLAVE: ROLL/PITCH/YAW/GYRO_XYZ
    SLAVE-->>SERIAL: TX: [01 03 18 data... CRC]
    SERIAL-->>HOST: regsToFloat() 解析浮点数

    Note over HOST,HW: === 写入控制 (FC06) ===

    HOST->>SERIAL: TX: [01 06 00 20 05 DC CRC]<br/>写 SERVO1 = 1500μs
    SERIAL->>SLAVE: USART2 RX
    SLAVE->>REG: eMBRegHoldingCB()<br/>mode=MB_REG_WRITE
    REG->>REG: is_reg_writable(0x0020)? ✅
    REG->>HW: apply_register()<br/>pwm_set_duty(SERVO1, 1500)
    HW-->>HW: TIM4_CH2 输出 1500μs
    SLAVE-->>SERIAL: TX: [01 06 00 20 05 DC CRC] (回显)
    SERIAL-->>HOST: 写入成功

    Note over HOST,HW: === 写保护 ===

    HOST->>SERIAL: TX: [01 06 00 00 xx xx CRC]<br/>尝试写 DEVICE_ID (只读)
    SERIAL->>SLAVE: USART2 RX
    SLAVE->>REG: is_reg_writable(0x0000)? ❌
    SLAVE-->>SERIAL: TX: [01 86 02 CRC]<br/>异常码 0x02
    SERIAL-->>HOST: 写入被拒绝

    Note over HOST,HW: === 后台传感器更新 ===

    loop 主循环 每 5ms
        HW->>REG: MS901M → 姿态浮点寄存器
        HW->>REG: ADC → 模拟量/电压/原始值
        HW->>REG: HAL_GetTick() → SYS_TICK
    end
